10 An act relating to exempting sales of building materials and supplies from
11 sales and use tax for priority housing projects
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 Sec. 1. 32 V.S.A. § 9743 is amended to read:
14 § 9743. ORGANIZATIONS NOT COVERED
15 Any sale, service, or admission to a place of entertainment charged by or to
16 any of the following or any use by any of the following are not subject to the
17 sales and use taxes imposed under this chapter:
18 * * *
19 (4)(A) Sales of building materials and supplies to be used in the
20 construction, reconstruction, alteration, remodeling, or repair of:
